'''綠原酸'''（{{lang-en|'''Chlorogenic acid'''}}，縮寫'''CGA'''），又名'''氯吉酸'''、'''氯原酸'''、'''咖啡单宁酸'''、'''杜仲绿原酸'''、'''全蝎提取物'''、'''咖啡酰奎尼酸'''等<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chemicalbook.com/ChemicalProductProperty_CN_CB2478906.htm |title=绿原酸 CAS: 327-97-9 |date=2016-08-05 |language=zh-hans |accessdate=2016-08-07 |archive-date=2016-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160814034831/http://www.chemicalbook.com/ChemicalProductProperty_CN_CB2478906.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是一天然的化合物，由[[咖啡酸|咖啡酸]]及(−)-[[奎寧酸|奎寧酸]][[酯|酯化]]而成。
綠原酸是一種重要的[[生物合成|生物合成]]中間體<ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1146/annurev.arplant.54.031902.134938 | title = Lignin biosynthesis | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_annual-review-of-plant-biology_2003_54/page/519 | year = 2003 | last1 = Boerjan | first1 = Wout | last2 = Ralph | first2 = John | last3 = Baucher | first3 = Marie | journal = [[Annual_Review_of_Plant_Biology|Annu. Rev. Plant Biol.]] | volume = 54 | pages = 519–46 | pmid = 14503002}}</ref>。綠原酸是[[木質素|木質素]]（{{lang|en|''lignin''}}）的[[木質素的生物合成|生物合成]]的重要中間生成物。綠原素作為一種[[抗氧化劑|抗氧化劑]]，可令餐後[[葡萄醣|葡萄醣]]釋出進入血液的過程減慢<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Johnston | first1 = K. L. | last2 = Clifford | first2 = M. N. | last3 = Morgan | first3 = L. M. | title = Coffee acutely modifies gastrointestinal hormone secretion and glucose tolerance in humans: glycemic effects of chlorogenic acid and caffeine | journal = {{tsl|en|The American Journal of Clinical Nutrition|Am. J. Clin. Nutrit.}} | volume = 78 | issue = 4 | pages = 728–733 | date = 2003-10 | url = http://www.ajcn.org/cgi/content/full/78/4/728 | pmid = 14522730 | language = en | access-date = 2016-08-07 | archive-date = 2010-04-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100421165842/http://www.ajcn.org/cgi/content/full/78/4/728 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

'''綠原酸'''這個名詞也泛指[[羥基肉桂酸|羥基肉桂酸]]（即：咖啡酸、[[阿魏酸|阿魏酸]]及[[对香豆酸|对香豆酸]]）與奎尼酸的酯化物<ref name="hierarchical">{{cite journal
