}}</ref>。

== 结构与性质 ==
綠原酸是[[咖啡酸|咖啡酸]]與<small>L</small>-[[奎尼酸|奎尼酸]]和3號位羥基縮合形成的[[酯|酯]]。<ref>{{cite journal
  | last1 = Clifford | first1 = M. N.
  | title = Chlorogenic acids and other cinnamates – nature, occurrence and dietary burden
  | journal = [[Journal_of_the_Science_of_Food_and_Agriculture|J. Sci. Food Agr.]]
  | volume = 79
  | pages = 362–372
  | year = 1999
  | doi = 10.1002/(SICI)1097-0010(19990301)79:3<362::AID-JSFA256>3.0.CO;2-D
  | issue = 3
}}</ref>綠原酸的異構體包括奎尼酸其它位置羥基酯化的產物，如4-''O''-咖啡酰奎尼酸（cryptochlorogenic acid或簡稱4-CQA）和5-''O''-咖啡酰奎尼酸（neochlorogenic acid或稱5-CQA，新綠原酸）。一位羥基的異構體尚未在自然界中發現。<ref name="hierarchical" />

兩個羥基被酯化則稱異綠原酸（isochlorogenic acid），存在於咖啡中。<ref>Isochlorogenic Acid. Isolation from Coffee and Structure Studies. H. M. Barnes, J. R. Feldman and W. V. White, J. Am. Chem. Soc., 1950, volume 72, issue 9, pages 4178–4182, {{doi|10.1021/ja01165a095}}</ref>例如3,4-二咖啡酰奎尼酸和3,5-二咖啡酰奎尼酸。<ref>{{cite journal
  | last1 = Corse | first1 = J.
  | last2 = Lundin | first2 = R. E.
  | last3 = Waiss | first3 = A. C.
  | title = Identification of several components of isochlorogenic acid
  | journal = [[Phytochemistry_(journal)|Phytochem.]]
  | volume = 4
  | issue = 3
  | pages = 527–529
  |date=May 1965
  | doi = 10.1016/S0031-9422(00)86209-3
}}</ref> 和1,5-二咖啡酰奎尼酸。

